# bjw-s Helm Charts

> Reusable Helm library chart and app-template for deploying applications on Kubernetes. Configuration is driven by a JSON Schema with full IDE autocompletion support.

The common library chart provides template functions for Deployments, StatefulSets, DaemonSets, CronJobs, Services, Ingress, PersistentVolumeClaims, ConfigMaps, Secrets, and more. The app-template chart wraps the library so you can deploy any application by providing values only.

